.Dt OPNSENSE-FETCH 8
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm opnsense-fetch
.Nd OPNsense fetch progress watcher
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Fl aq
.Op Fl o Ar file
.Op Fl T Ar timeout
.Ar url
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
utility passes all known arguments to
.Xr fetch 1
and produces progress output as long as the download runs in the
background.
